{"tid":1415044,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"收皮啦!!!一芳中國茶","createTime":"2019-08-05T13:08:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T09:10:15.000Z","uid":198361,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d3023c068225aada034e3b9ab99855369bfafb52","tid":1415044,"uid":198361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:08:09.000Z","msg":"香港市民今（5）日發起「三罷」（罷工、罷課、罷市）運動以及不合作運動。「一芳台灣水果茶」在微博指出，除個別政府建議，處於示威遊行核心區的門店外，一芳香港20家門店壓力下堅持營<span style=\"color: red;\">「堅決維護一國兩制，堅決反對暴力罷工」</span>。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vBH6D34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvBH6D34.jpg&h=ed182ed0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我哋都有個收皮活動等緊你!"},{"pid":"65c4cff309fe27d74cbd045b5a6afeb808643f59","tid":1415044,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:08:59.000Z","msg":"台獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d7d6b7a987c6e7f9974141c25ce0b7e599a05b3","tid":1415044,"uid":119361,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:09:17.000Z","msg":"想變成吉野家咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d9e336c76dec50e96b794728c3b44064a067f4","tid":1415044,"uid":282046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:10:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ee3bbe184ab9e25babc87f65b5e16e6d61b2d07","tid":1415044,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:23:58.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"a059090ef716e8828667fc2b14f0ba5485cbc05c","tid":1415044,"uid":293897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8d9e336c76dec50e96b794728c3b44064a067f4","tid":1415044,"uid":282046,"